speechtext:
Motion No. 33
That Bill C-26 be amended in Clause 22 by adding immediately after line 14 at page 12 the following:
"(2) In applying subsection (1) Treasury Board shall, in the deployment of an employee, include in its direction the following factors:
(a)	the need to develop the employee through additional work experience;
(b)	the demonstrated need to fill a vacancy on an immediate basis;
(c)	the demonstrated needs of both the employee and management and;
(d)	compassionate grounds."
